    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so you can just hop in and go. It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you!",
      "price": 33500.0,
