    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. This car has been garage-kept and treated with the utmost care, showing only minor cosmetic wear consistent with responsible use. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, while the interior features premium leather upholstery that remains supple and free of tears or odors. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health; I have kept a comprehensive log of all services, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the navigation system, functions exactly as intended. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer who values a documented history and mechanical peace of mind.",
      "price": 38500.0,
