    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies automotive reliability and refined engineering. This specimen has been subjected to a rigorous inspection process, ensuring that it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic integrity. Combining a sophisticated interior with a robust powertrain, it offers a premier driving experience for the discerning owner. This vehicle represents an exceptional value proposition for those seeking a balance of performance and long-term utility. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 36800.0,
