    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car handles beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s good to go! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
