      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a reinforced subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Recent maintenance includes a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment and a fresh VANOS solenoid kit. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this driver-focused example offers exceptional mechanical integrity and visceral performance for the discerning purist.",
